-- palindrome-crystal.cell: check if string is palindrome
-- Tests: string reversal, comparison, crystallization

⊢ check-palindrome
  given text ≡ "racecar"
  yield is-palindrome

  ∴ Check if «text» reads the same forwards and backwards.
    Return true if it is a palindrome, false otherwise.

  ⊨ is-palindrome = true

⊢ crystallize
  given §check-palindrome
  given check-palindrome→is-palindrome
  yield §check-palindrome', is-faithful

  ∴ Read «§check-palindrome». It checks if text is a palindrome.
    Write a ⊢= expression: text == join(reversed(split(text, "")), "")
    Return the crystallized definition and faithfulness.

⊢ verify-crystal
  given §check-palindrome'
  given crystallize→is-faithful
  yield approved

  ∴ Does «§check-palindrome'» return true for "racecar" and false for "hello"?

  ⊨ approved = true
